<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Become an Affiliate | ScriptZon</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/dashboard.css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">
</head>
<body>
  <div class="dashboard-container">
    <main class="main-content">
      <div class="content-wrapper">
        <div class="page-header">
          <h1>Become an Affiliate</h1>
        </div>
        
        <% if(error_msg != '') { %>
          <div class="alert alert-danger">
            <%= error_msg %>
          </div>
        <% } %>
        
        <div class="account-section">
          <h2>Join Our Affiliate Program</h2>
          <p>Earn 30% recurring commission on every subscription from users you refer to ScriptZon!</p>
          
          <div class="affiliate-benefits">
            <div class="benefit-item">
              <div class="benefit-icon">
                <i class="fas fa-percentage"></i>
              </div>
              <div class="benefit-content">
                <h3>30% Recurring Commission</h3>
                <p>Earn 30% of every payment your referrals make, for as long as they remain subscribed.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="benefit-item">
              <div class="benefit-icon">
                <i class="fas fa-money-bill-wave"></i>
              </div>
              <div class="benefit-content">
                <h3>Lifetime Earnings</h3>
                <p>Get paid for the entire lifetime of your referred customers' subscriptions.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="benefit-item">
              <div class="benefit-icon">
                <i class="fas fa-link"></i>
              </div>
              <div class="benefit-content">
                <h3>Easy Sharing</h3>
                <p>Get your unique referral link and share it on social media, email, or your website.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="commission-examples">
            <h3>Potential Earnings</h3>
            <div class="example-grid">
              <div class="example-card">
                <div class="example-header">5 Referrals</div>
                <div class="example-body">
                  <p>Monthly Plan: <strong>$28.50/month</strong></p>
                  <p>Annual Plan: <strong>$148.50/year</strong></p>
                </div>
              </div>
              
              <div class="example-card">
                <div class="example-header">10 Referrals</div>
                <div class="example-body">
                  <p>Monthly Plan: <strong>$57.00/month</strong></p>
                  <p>Annual Plan: <strong>$297.00/year</strong></p>
                </div>
              </div>
              
              <div class="example-card">
                <div class="example-header">20 Referrals</div>
                <div class="example-body">
                  <p>Monthly Plan: <strong>$114.00/month</strong></p>
                  <p>Annual Plan: <strong>$594.00/year</strong></p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="affiliate-join-cta">
            <form action="/affiliates/join" method="POST">
              <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary btn-large">Join Affiliate Program</button>
            </form>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="account-section">
          <h2>How It Works</h2>
          <div class="steps">
            <div class="step">
              <div class="step-number">1</div>
              <div class="step-content">
                <h3>Join the Program</h3>
                <p>Click the button above to join our affiliate program and get your unique referral link.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="step">
              <div class="step-number">2</div>
              <div class="step-content">
                <h3>Share Your Link</h3>
                <p>Share your referral link with your audience through social media, email, or your website.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="step">
              <div class="step-number">3</div>
              <div class="step-content">
                <h3>Earn Commissions</h3>
                <p>When someone signs up and subscribes through your link, you earn 30% of their subscription fee.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="account-section">
          <h2>Affiliate FAQ</h2>
          <div class="faq-grid">
            <div class="faq-item">
              <h3>When do I get paid?</h3>
              <p>Commissions are calculated at the end of each month and paid out by the 15th of the following month.</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="faq-item">
              <h3>Is there a minimum payout threshold?</h3>
              <p>Yes, you need to earn at least $50 in commissions before a payout is processed.</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="faq-item">
              <h3>How long does the referral cookie last?</h3>
              <p>Our referral cookies last for 30 days, giving your referrals plenty of time to sign up.</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="faq-item">
              <h3>Can I promote ScriptZon on multiple platforms?</h3>
              <p>Yes! You can share your referral link on any platform where you have an audience.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </main>
  </div>

  <script src="/js/dashboard.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
